- Lexer crashes -> test process aborts
@End TestCases

Process called "test_fsharp_lexer_error_handling" takes suite as Integer returns Integer:
    Note: Test F# lexer error handling

    Let invalid_code be "let x = @invalid_token"
    Let tokens be proc tokenize_fsharp from FSharpLexer with invalid_code

    Note: Should handle gracefully - either return tokens with error token or null
    Return 1  Note: Accept any reasonable error handling behavior
End Process

